#: ../../../how-to/postgrest.md:7
msgid ""
"Create data in PostgreSQL, provide it as an API using PostgREST, and then "
"easily create an **\"API for convenient data search\"**. This is a "
"beginner's guide to PostgREST with PGroonga."
